# Vector/graph store JSONL data files are tracked via git-lfs (see
# .gitattributes) so a deployed instance actually ships with real data
# instead of an empty vector store -- only the runtime lock files (created
# by JsonlVectorStore's cross-process file lock) are excluded.
**/datasets/vector_embeddings/*.jsonl.lock
